About the game:

The SFA (Space Femme Arsenal) has announced its top 2 star port pilots: USA's Lacey Jones and Russia's Nikita Volkov, both top gunwomen at the esteemed 'Apocalypse' Academy located 1.5 light years above Zurich, Switzerland. Both women have survived SEAL Space Camp in their respective orbital colonies and now join forces to defend Earth against enemy invasion. Fly as either pilot and blow aliens away!
